Lock region.Once set region values cannot be modified.
Enable region.A value of 0xA enables, others disable.

register.description: The FW Region 0 Channel 62 Permission 0 Register defines the permissions for the slave mmr.dru_mmr_cfg region 0 channel 62 firewall.
